articles.author: Samantha Murphy Kelly
articles.title: iPhone 15 hits shelves around the world. Here’s what you need to know - CNN
articles.description: Apple’s iPhone 15 lineup hit stores Friday as people waited in long lines across China, Europe and the US to be among the first to get their hands on one of the company’s next-generation smartphones.
